This package is the shared developer SDK for the Thebes Layer 1 example dapps.
It bundles a browser boundary client, a Memphis passkey auth client, a typed
React layer, and a Motoko backend library. It builds on the Internet Computer
Canister Development Kit (IC CDK) and the Motoko core library:

